<body>
<cb:div>
<pb n="0149a" xml:id="I01.0058.0149a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0149a00" type="honorific"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><cb:docNumber>No. 58</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0149a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>李清造報德像碑</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="I" n="0149a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0149a0101">大齊天保六年歲次乙亥七月己卯朔二日庚辰。鄉郡鄉縣李清言。蓋聞益天之明者。莫若於日月。益人之
<lb ed="I" n="0149a02" type="honorific"/>善者。莫若於脩福。是以一<note n="0149001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">飡＝餐【史】</note><note n="0149001" resp="ihp" type="mod">飡【佛拓】，餐【史】</note><app n="0149001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">餐</lem><rdg wit="【原】">飡</rdg></app>之惠。<note n="0149002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">㚘＝扶【史】</note><note n="0149002" resp="ihp" type="mod">㚘【佛拓】，扶【史】</note><app n="0149002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">扶</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㚘</rdg></app>輪之報。為前<note n="0149003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30840"/>＝兗【史】</note><note n="0149003" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30840"/>【佛拓】，兗【史】</note><app n="0149003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">兗</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30840"/></rdg></app>雍七兵尚書陽冀定五州刺史義同文靜公趙郡李憲。
<lb ed="I" n="0149a03" type="honorific"/>司空文簡公李希宗。二公父子。以<note n="0149004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">礼＝禮【史】</note><note n="0149004" resp="ihp" type="mod">礼【佛拓】，禮【史】</note><app n="0149004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">禮</lem><rdg wit="【原】">礼</rdg></app>待青。得奉朝請。而青德乏故賢。無刎頸之報。去家五百里。<note n="0149005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30866"/>＝就【史】</note><note n="0149005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30866"/>【佛拓】，就【史】</note><app n="0149005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">就</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30866"/></rdg></app><note n="0149006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𨙷＝阱【史】</note><note n="0149006" resp="ihp" type="mod">𨙷【佛拓】，阱【史】</note><app n="0149006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">阱</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𨙷</rdg></app><note n="0149007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">耶＝陘【史】</note><note n="0149007" resp="ihp" type="mod">耶【佛拓】，陘【史】</note><app n="0149007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">陘</lem><rdg wit="【原】">耶</rdg></app>關榆。
<lb ed="I" n="0149a04" type="honorific"/>交<note n="0149008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30842"/>＝式【史】</note><note n="0149008" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30842"/>【佛拓】，式【史】</note><app n="0149008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">式</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30842"/></rdg></app>万里萇途。百州路側。造報德像碑。磨巖刊石。万世不<note n="0149009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30864"/>＝朽【史】</note><note n="0149009" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30864"/>【佛拓】，朽【史】</note><app n="0149009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">朽</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30864"/></rdg></app>。東越海崖。西過秦<note n="0149010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30843"/>＝壟【史】</note><note n="0149010" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30843"/>【佛拓】，壟【史】</note><app n="0149010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">壟</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30843"/></rdg></app>。車馬<note n="0149011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30844"/>＝殷【史】</note><note n="0149011" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30844"/>【佛拓】，殷【史】</note><app n="0149011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">殷</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30844"/></rdg></app>上。無日不有云尒。
<lb ed="I" n="0149a05" type="honorific"/>夫乾<note n="0149012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">巛＝坤【史】</note><note n="0149012" resp="ihp" type="mod">巛【佛拓】，坤【史】</note><app n="0149012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">坤</lem><rdg wit="【原】">巛</rdg></app>以簡易可久。聖賢以<note n="0149013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">㑅＝作【史】</note><note n="0149013" resp="ihp" type="mod">㑅【佛拓】，作【史】</note><app n="0149013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">作</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㑅</rdg></app>述為大。麗天標懸像之用。鎮地表成務之功。顯晦唯丈人之迹。語嘿蓋君子
<lb ed="I" n="0149a06" type="honorific"/>之道。二經混其無為。五緯彰其區別。仰觀俯則。遠物近身。<note n="0149014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30845"/>＝備【史】</note><note n="0149014" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30845"/>【佛拓】，備【史】</note><app n="0149014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">備</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30845"/></rdg></app>諸<note n="0149015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30846"/>＝禽【史】</note><note n="0149015" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30846"/>【佛拓】，禽【史】</note><app n="0149015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">禽</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30846"/></rdg></app>跡。可<note n="0149016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">畧＝略【史】</note><note n="0149016" resp="ihp" type="mod">畧【佛拓】，略【史】</note><app n="0149016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">略</lem><rdg wit="【原】">畧</rdg></app>言矣。至於六十四卦。藏用顯仁。言
<lb ed="I" n="0149a07" type="honorific"/>先王者。主於聖王。言后者。通諸群后。言<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">大</unclear>人者。大有聖德之人。言君子者。<note n="0149017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB13415"/>＝博【史】</note><note n="0149017" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB13415"/>【佛拓】，博【史】</note><app n="0149017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">博</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB13415"/></rdg></app>閞有德。三百五篇。無<note n="0149018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">耶＝邪【史】</note><note n="0149018" resp="ihp" type="mod">耶【佛拓】，邪【史】</note><app n="0149018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邪</lem><rdg wit="【原】">耶</rdg></app>以<note n="0149019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB17073"/>＝蔽【史】</note><note n="0149019" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB17073"/>【佛拓】，蔽【史】</note><app n="0149019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">蔽</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB17073"/></rdg></app>。皆
<lb ed="I" n="0149a08" type="honorific"/>欲納民軌物。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">其</unclear>於<note n="0149020" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30357"/>＝克【史】</note><note n="0149020" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30357"/>【佛拓】，克【史】</note><app n="0149020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">克</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30357"/></rdg></app>己復<app type="star" corresp="#0149004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">禮</lem><rdg wit="【原】">礼</rdg></app>。方之釋典。曾何髣髴。岱宗小宇宙。<note n="0149021" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">浘＝尾【史】</note><note n="0149021" resp="ihp" type="mod">浘【佛拓】，尾【史】</note><app n="0149021"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">尾</lem><rdg wit="【原】">浘</rdg></app><note n="0149022" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𤁵＝閭【史】</note><note n="0149022" resp="ihp" type="mod">𤁵【佛拓】，閭【史】</note><app n="0149022"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">閭</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𤁵</rdg></app>狹秋水。較之未舉馬豪。察之殊少麟角。
<lb ed="I" n="0149a09" type="honorific"/>愛河湛〃。掬指於舟中。朽宅炎〃。<note n="0149023" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">爤＝爛【史】</note><note n="0149023" resp="ihp" type="mod">爤【佛拓】，爛【史】</note><app n="0149023"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">爛</lem><rdg wit="【原】">爤</rdg></app>額於車下。方知誓願<note n="0149024" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30357"/>＝剋【史】</note><note n="0149024" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30357"/>【佛拓】，剋【史】</note><app n="0149024"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">剋</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30357"/></rdg></app>成。降鑒世<note n="0149025" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30847"/>＝界【史】</note><note n="0149025" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30847"/>【佛拓】，界【史】</note><app n="0149025"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">界</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30847"/></rdg></app>。慈忍既<app type="star" corresp="#0149005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">就</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30866"/></rdg></app>。視現王宮。放光明於大
<lb ed="I" n="0149a10" type="honorific"/>千。燎華燈於深夜。陽九<app type="star" corresp="#0149013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">作</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㑅</rdg></app>沴。濡足於堯年。<note n="0149026" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">隂＝陰【史】</note><note n="0149026" resp="ihp" type="mod">隂【佛拓】，陰【史】</note><app n="0149026"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">陰</lem><rdg wit="【原】">隂</rdg></app>六為<note n="0149027" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30870"/>＝災【史】</note><note n="0149027" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30870"/>【佛拓】，災【史】</note><app n="0149027"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">災</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30870"/></rdg></app>。授手於湯日。覆載比兩儀。亭毒<note n="0149028" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30849"/>＝猶【史】</note><note n="0149028" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30849"/>【佛拓】，猶【史】</note><app n="0149028"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">猶</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30849"/></rdg></app>一子。擾擾四生。<note n="0149029" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">軄＝職【史】</note><note n="0149029" resp="ihp" type="mod">軄【佛拓】，職【史】</note><app n="0149029"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">職</lem><rdg wit="【原】">軄</rdg></app>〃
<lb ed="I" n="0149a11" type="honorific"/>三<app type="star" corresp="#0149025"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">界</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30847"/></rdg></app>。何止拱之如北極。仰之如東君者乎。若迺千里一曲之河。派崑崙而屬牛斗。方舟避風之水。<note n="0149030" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">噵＝導【史】</note><note n="0149030" resp="ihp" type="mod">噵【佛拓】，導【史】</note><app n="0149030"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">導</lem><rdg wit="【原】">噵</rdg></app>岷峨而
<lb ed="I" n="0149a12" type="honorific"/><note n="0149031" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30850"/>＝直【史】</note><note n="0149031" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30850"/>【佛拓】，直【史】</note><app n="0149031"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">直</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30850"/></rdg></app>井絡。連城之寶。必挺於楚山。照車之珍。宜產於隨國。馬形<note n="0149032" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30473"/>＝淑【史】</note><note n="0149032" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30473"/>【佛拓】，淑【史】</note><app n="0149032"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">淑</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30473"/></rdg></app>問。<app type="star" corresp="#0149024"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">剋</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30357"/></rdg></app>昌於千古。<note n="0149033" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30851"/>＝龍【史】</note><note n="0149033" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30851"/>【佛拓】，龍【史】</note><app n="0149033"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">龍</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30851"/></rdg></app>德淳風。必祀於百世。懷月
<lb ed="I" n="0149a13" type="honorific"/>動夢。嗽天成祉。類任姒之興周。等<app type="star" corresp="#0149026"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">陰</lem><rdg wit="【原】">隂</rdg></app>馬之隆漢。光遠彌燿。條布增芳。非積祜之餘榮。其熟能興於此。今
<lb ed="I" n="0149a14" type="honorific"/>皇　后趙國栢仁縣永寧鄉<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">陰</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">灌</unclear>里人也。分裂山河之盛。懷握瑾瑜之美。史無闕文。我略辭費。祖儀同文靜
<lb ed="I" n="0149a15" type="honorific"/>公。金<note n="0149034" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30852"/>＝相【史】</note><note n="0149034" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30852"/>【佛拓】，相【史】</note><app n="0149034"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">相</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30852"/></rdg></app>玉<note n="0149035" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">筫＝質【史】</note><note n="0149035" resp="ihp" type="mod">筫【佛拓】，質【史】</note><app n="0149035"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">質</lem><rdg wit="【原】">筫</rdg></app>。取貴當年。考司空文簡公。桂茂蘭薰。名揚身後。唯此公二。先聖所遵。<note n="0149036" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30853"/>＝復【史】</note><note n="0149036" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30853"/>【佛拓】，復【史】</note><app n="0149036"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">復</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30853"/></rdg></app>皇欽德葉。各產子十人。
<lb ed="I" n="0149a16" type="honorific"/>五男五女。再世如一。男懷衛珍王承之操。咸體潤珪璋。女履恭姜伯姬之節。皆心貞琬琰。至如馬族丈夫。五
<lb ed="I" n="0149a17" type="honorific"/>常取目。璩氏婦人。三賢擅美。何<note n="0149037" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">笇＝算【史】</note><note n="0149037" resp="ihp" type="mod">笇【佛拓】，算【史】</note><app n="0149037"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">算</lem><rdg wit="【原】">笇</rdg></app>張鉤。子孫繁盛。黃羊白環。<note n="0149038" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">㣧＝胤【史】</note><note n="0149038" resp="ihp" type="mod">㣧【佛拓】，胤【史】</note><app n="0149038"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">胤</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㣧</rdg></app>嗣丕顯。論家語德。我實兼之。有姓名者。承華
<lb ed="I" n="0149a18" type="honorific"/>遠葉。分流濬源。附驥尾而絕塵。託龍髯而高翥。乘車食肉。不<note n="0149039" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30867"/>＝假【史】</note><note n="0149039" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30867"/>【佛拓】，假【史】</note><app n="0149039"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">假</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30867"/></rdg></app>長鋏之謠。<note n="0149040" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30855"/>＝升【史】</note><note n="0149040" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30855"/>【佛拓】，升【史】</note><app n="0149040"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">升</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30855"/></rdg></app>堂入室。無勞囊錐之請。<note n="0149041" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30856"/>＝葭【史】</note><note n="0149041" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30856"/>【佛拓】，葭【史】</note><app n="0149041"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">葭</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30856"/></rdg></app>莩之
<lb ed="I" n="0149a19" type="honorific"/><note n="0149042" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30871"/>＝親【史】</note><note n="0149042" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30871"/>【佛拓】，親【史】</note><app n="0149042"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">親</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30871"/></rdg></app>。迺枝遙十世。丘山之顧。則潤過九里。朝履清階。鄉居右<app type="star" corresp="#0149029"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">職</lem><rdg wit="【原】">軄</rdg></app>增榮改價。二公之造<note n="0149043" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𤇟＝焉【史】</note><note n="0149043" resp="ihp" type="mod">𤇟【佛拓】，焉【史】</note><app n="0149043"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">焉</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𤇟</rdg></app>。加以宿殖善因。洞悟空
<lb ed="I" n="0149a20" type="honorific"/><app type="star" corresp="#0149039"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">假</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30867"/></rdg></app>。投軀正覺。傾心大乘。體瞬息〃之不<note n="0149044" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">㽞＝留【史】</note><note n="0149044" resp="ihp" type="mod">㽞【佛拓】，留【史】</note><app n="0149044"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">留</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㽞</rdg></app>。識泡炎之必盡。營資<note n="0149045" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">粮＝糧【史】</note><note n="0149045" resp="ihp" type="mod">粮【佛拓】，糧【史】</note><app n="0149045"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">糧</lem><rdg wit="【原】">粮</rdg></app>於曠路。樹功業於福田。初未脫於生死。終不
<lb ed="I" n="0149a21" type="honorific"/>離於苦空。波輪迴。星流電滅。昔孔丘既歿。子貢六年不返。向苗已逝。始春三載不歸戶。改辭曹門通德。召奭
<lb ed="I" n="0149a22" type="honorific"/>甘棠勿<note n="0149046" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30872"/>＝剪【史】</note><note n="0149046" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30872"/>【佛拓】，剪【史】</note><app n="0149046"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">剪</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30872"/></rdg></app>。韓<note n="0149047" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30858"/>＝起【史】</note><note n="0149047" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30858"/>【佛拓】，起【史】</note><app n="0149047"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">起</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30858"/></rdg></app>嘉樹無忘。<note n="0149048" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30873"/>＝竊【史】</note><note n="0149048" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30873"/>【佛拓】，竊【史】</note><app n="0149048"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">竊</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30873"/></rdg></app>以石槨<note n="0149049" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">蜄＝蜃【史】</note><note n="0149049" resp="ihp" type="mod">蜄【佛拓】，蜃【史】</note><app n="0149049"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">蜃</lem><rdg wit="【原】">蜄</rdg></app>炭。無益於速<app type="star" corresp="#0149009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">朽</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30864"/></rdg></app>。珠<note n="0149050" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30859"/>＝襦【史】</note><note n="0149050" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30859"/>【佛拓】，襦【史】</note><app n="0149050"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">襦</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30859"/></rdg></app>玉匣。有加於戮尸。鑒覆車於往塗。思改轍於今
<lb ed="I" n="0149a23" type="honorific"/>軌。負土城墳之力。用於鷲山。傳蘭薦菊之財。施於鹿野。斯則之先覺<app type="star" corresp="#0149013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">作</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㑅</rdg></app>範。後昆有義存<app type="star" corresp="#0149043"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">焉</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𤇟</rdg></app>。可不尚歟。民無德
<lb ed="I" n="0149a24" type="honorific"/>而稱<app type="star" corresp="#0149043"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">焉</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𤇟</rdg></app>。烏菟輪<note n="0149051" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30860"/>＝虧【史】</note><note n="0149051" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30860"/>【佛拓】，虧【史】</note><app n="0149051"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虧</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30860"/></rdg></app>。寒暑迴復。滄海為原。水將湛於金<note n="0149052" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">㓻＝剛【史】</note><note n="0149052" resp="ihp" type="mod">㓻【佛拓】，剛【史】</note><app n="0149052"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">剛</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㓻</rdg></app>。火垂㙩於華想。式刊鼎鼐。永<app type="star" corresp="#0149013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">作</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㑅</rdg></app>橋<note n="0149053" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30861"/>＝樑【史】</note><note n="0149053" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30861"/>【佛拓】，樑【史】</note><app n="0149053"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">樑</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30861"/></rdg></app>。其詞曰。
<lb ed="I" n="0149a25" type="honorific"/>管窺行健。蠡測泉流。真蹤遐闊。<note n="0149054" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𨐧＝壁【史】</note><note n="0149054" resp="ihp" type="mod">𨐧【佛拓】，壁【史】</note><app n="0149054"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">壁</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𨐧</rdg></app>此披求。惟彼　調御。鑒我閻浮。揚舲沸海。舉燭重幽。注水不竭。傳火逾<app type="star" corresp="#0149044"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">留</lem><rdg wit="【原】">㽞</rdg></app>。
<lb ed="I" n="0149a26" type="honorific"/>明懸離坎。德邁迴游。滔滔甕口。巖〃峰石。合浦<note n="0149055" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𠇹＝俓【史】</note><note n="0149055" resp="ihp" type="mod">𠇹【佛拓】，俓【史】</note><app n="0149055"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">俓</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𠇹</rdg></app>寸。藍田盈尺。汁光失<note n="0149056" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30863"/>＝序【史】</note><note n="0149056" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30863"/>【佛拓】，序【史】</note><app n="0149056"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">序</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30863"/></rdg></app>。蒼積承庴。我有微音。正位宮掖。<app type="star" corresp="#0149042"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">親</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30871"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0149a27" type="honorific"/>試經典。躬勞紡<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">績</unclear>。高涯斯潤。長瀾增激。箕裘不墜。冠蓋成林。家藏桓玉。世挺南金。男賢慕簡。女潔還<app type="star" corresp="#0149026"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">陰</lem><rdg wit="【原】">隂</rdg></app>。十六
<lb ed="I" n="0149a28" type="honorific"/>比德。二義齊音。俱停万頃。競竦千尋。指掌拾芥。跨古騰今。爰有宗人。老成夙惠。託生正識。投誠真諦。食椹泮
<lb ed="I" n="0149a29" type="honorific"/>林。庇<app type="star" corresp="#0149026"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">陰</lem><rdg wit="【原】">隂</rdg></app>藂桂。薄言報德。營斯莊麗。功□造。推心弘濟。陳信貞石。傳芳來裳。空聞海竭。熟俟河清。鄛駒易住。目
<lb ed="I" n="0149a30" type="honorific"/>鳥難停。春水始泮。水綠山青。秋風□蕭。葉下霜明。民非城是。淵實丘平。嗟〃後世。識此生榮。　燕州釋仙書</p>
